title: Eddie Campbell - Bacchus Books 1-10
description:
Very much looking forward to the two Omnibus print editions of this (you can pre-order the first one right here http://www.topshelfcomix.com/catalog/bacchus/619 ). It looks like they're the same size and design as 'Alec - The Years Have Pants', which will make them look mighty fine on a bookshelf next to each other.

---------------------------------------------------------

Bacchus

Written and Illustrated by Eddie Campbell

Each volume has extensive, clear notes on the back page explaining where the comics were originally printed, when they were printed, as well as where they have been previously collected.

Top Shelf Productions, 2014

Books 1 & 2, 205 pages
Immortality Isn't Forever
The Gods of Business

Books 3 & 4, 260 pages
Doing the Islands with Bacchus
Eyeball Kid: One Man Show

Books 5 & 6, 237 pages
Earth Water Air and Fire
The 1001 Nights of Bacchus

Books 7 & 8, 162 pages
Hermes Versus the Eyeball Kid
The Picture of Doreen Grey

Books 9 & 10, 280 pages
King Bacchus
Banged Up

If you feel so inclined, please go here http://www.topshelfcomix.com/ and buy their really cool stuff. That way they, like, ya know, keep making more really cool stuff
